description: Primes p such that x^3 = 2 has more than one solution mod p and the sum of the (three) solutions is 2*p.
comments: Subsequence of A040028 and of A014752, complement of A059899 relative to A014752. Solutions mod p are represented by integers from 0 to p-1.
author: _Klaus Brockhaus_, Mar 02 2001
